welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Catonsville! This charming city is known for its quaint shops, delicious local cuisine, and friendly community. We invite you to explore and discover all that Catonsville has to offer. Enjoy your stay!"

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Baltimore/Washington International Thurgood Marshall Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Concourse A
terminals.description: Concourse A at Baltimore/Washington International Thurgood Marshall Airport primarily serves domestic flights.

terminals.name: Concourse B
terminals.description: Concourse B at Baltimore/Washington International Thurgood Marshall Airport primarily serves international flights.

terminals.name: Concourse C
terminals.description: Concourse C at Baltimore/Washington International Thurgood Marshall Airport serves a mix of domestic and international flights.

wifi.note: Free Wi-Fi is available throughout the airport. No password is required.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: This terminal serves all commercial flights and houses the check-in counters, security checkpoints, and gates.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: This terminal is exclusively for private and charter flights, providing a more luxurious and personalized experience.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.
